      "name": "Relative Hemolysis Index comparison — multi-site perfusion centre campaign",
      "description": "CFD-predicted RHI values for all five flow-speed operating points were compared against measured RHI data collected across five clinical perfusion centres. Predicted RHI remained below 1.0 for all points; maximum discrepancy was 8.3%. The multi-site data collection is characterised in the assessment narrative as providing controlled experimental benchmarks equivalent to a purpose-designed laboratory experiment, supporting the inference that the controlled-experiment requirement is satisfied.",
      "wasGeneratedBy": {
